tedPerson1-5\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>RelatedPerson</h5></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><code>http://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cds/StructureDefinition/cds-fr-related-person</code></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>create</code>, <code>update</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h5 id=\"en-Organization1-6\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>Organization</h5></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href=\"https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/1.0.1/StructureDefinition-as-organization.html\">AS Organization Profileversion: 1.0.1)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Supported Profiles</span><p><code>http://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cds/StructureDefinition/cds-organization</code></p></div><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>create</code>, <code>update</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h5 id=\"en-Device1-7\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>Device</h5></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html\">Deviceversion: 4.0.1)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>create</code>, <code>update</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h5 id=\"en-DocumentReference1-8\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>DocumentReference</h5></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-cdl-document-reference.html\">DocumentReference Cahier de Liaisonversion: 3.0.1)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li><strong>MAY</strong> support <code>delete</code>.</li><li>Supports <code>update</code>, <code>delete</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/></div></div></div><h3 id=\"en-rest2\">REST Configuration: 2 </h3><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"en-mode2\" class=\"panel-title\">Mode: <code>client</code></h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div><p>Alimente le cahier de liaison avec une nouvelle note</p>\n</div><div class=\"lead\"><em>Security</em></div><blockquote><div><p>L’ANS propose des référentiels dédiés à la politique de sécurité (la PGSSI-S\n) et des mécanismes de sécurisation sont définis dans les volets de la couche Transport du Cadre d’Interopérabilité des systèmes\nd’information de santé (CI-SIS)</p>\n</div></blockquote><div class=\"lead\"><em>Summary of System-wide Interactions</em></div><ul><li>Supports the <code>transaction</code>interaction described as follows:<div><p>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cdl/StructureDefinition/cdl-bundle-creation-note</p>\n</div></li><li>Supports the <code>transaction</code>interaction described as follows:<div><p>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cdl/StructureDefinition/cdl-bundle-maj-note</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div><h4 id=\"en-resourcesCap2\">Capabilities by Resource/Profile</h4><h5 id=\"en-resourcesSummary2\">Summary</h5><p>The summary table lists the resources that are part of this configuration, and for each resource it lists:</p><ul><li>The relevant profiles (if any)</li><li>The interactions supported by each resource (<b><span class=\"bg-info\">R</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">S</span></b>earch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">U</span></b>pdate, and <b><span class=\"bg-info\">C</span></b>reate, are always shown, while <b><span class=\"bg-info\">VR</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">P</span></b>atch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">D</span></b>elete, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">I</span></b>nstance, or <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">T</span></b>ype are only present if at least one of the resources has support for them.</li><li><span>The required, recommended, and some optional search parameters (if any). </span></li><li>The linked resources enabled for <code>_include</code></li><li>The other resources enabled for <code>_revinclude</code></li><li>The operations on the resource (if any)</li></ul><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th><b>Resource Type</b></th><th><b>Profile</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET a resource (read interaction)\">R</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET all set of resources of the type (search interaction)\">S</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"PUT a new resource version (update interaction)\">U</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"POST a new resource (create interaction)\">C</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"DELETE a resource (delete interaction)\">D</b></th><th><b title=\"Required and recommended search parameters\">Searches</b></th><th><code><b>_include</b></code></th><th><code><b>_revinclude</b></code></th><th><b>Operations</b></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Bundle2-1\">Bundle</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-cdl-bundle-creation-note.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cdl/StructureDefinition/cdl-bundle-creation-note|3.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Patient2-2\">Patient</a></td><td><a href=\"https://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/2.0.1/StructureDefinition-fr-core-patient.html\">https://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/StructureDefinition/fr-core-patient|2.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Practitioner2-3\">Practitioner</a></td><td><a href=\"https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/1.0.1/StructureDefinition-as-practitioner.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/StructureDefinition/as-practitioner|1.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-PractitionerRole2-4\">PractitionerRole</a></td><td><a href=\"https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/1.0.1/StructureDefinition-as-practitionerrole.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/StructureDefinition/as-practitionerrole|1.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-RelatedPerson2-5\">RelatedPerson</a></td><td>http://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cds/StructureDefinition/cds-fr-related-person</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Device2-6\">Device</a></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html\">http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/Device|4.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Organization2-7\">Organization</a></td><td><a href=\"https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/1.0.1/StructureDefinition-as-organization.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/StructureDefinition/as-organization|1.0.1</a><br/><em>Additional supported profiles:</em><br/>  <code>http://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cds/StructureDefinition/cds-organization</code></td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-DocumentReference2-8\">DocumentReference</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-cdl-document-reference.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cdl/StructureDefinition/cdl-document-reference|3.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\">y<span title=\"MAY\">y?</span></td><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr></tbody></table></div><hr